    • onActionUpdateAppointment

      public void onActionUpdateAppointment(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent) throws IOException
      This method will take the user to the UpdateAppointmentView. On action this changes views to the UpdateAppointmentView. The selectedAppointment will be sent to the UpdateAppointmentView so the fields and combo boxes can be populated with the correct information. This method calls upon my Lambda Expression that is declared in this class. The lambda expression creates an alertError box. I used a lambda here to reduce redundancy in my code.
      Parameters:
      actionEvent -
      Throws:
      IOException
